Company Description                    




                        Dr. Peng Telecom & Media Group Co., Ltd.  is an information technology and services company based out of Chengdu. It is mainly engaged in telecommunication services. It provides internet services, broadband access services, server custody, data storage, security and monitoring, operation of image monitoring systems, advertising etc.                    


